data.description: This solid brick home exudes warmth & comfort, combining 100-yr-old craftsmanship w/ modern amenities & finishes. Custom window benches & a vent-free gas fireplace make the LR a cozy retreat while the newly restained woodwork & hardwood flooring add even more charm. The DR features a wet bar complete with mini-fridge & marble countertops. An original floor to ceiling pantry beautifully juxtaposes the newly refaced cabinets, granite countertops, SS appliances, tiled backsplash & flooring updates in the kitchen. This functional space opens to a newly added 1st floor laundry/mudroom. The primary bdrm features vanity & office built-ins that flank the fireplace as well as a tailor-made barn door. 3 more bdrms finish off the level - 1 of which is captive & includes a built-in bed & shelving. A 3rd fl bonus space is accessed via a ladder staircase & offers the possibility of 2 additional bdrms. Outside a herringbone paver patio, a pergola, and a stunning fireplace/grill combo are sure to wow.
